#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/mark_align_pcb.rst:2
msgid "标记 / 对齐 PCB"
msgstr "Mark / Align PCB"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/mark_align_pcb.rst:4
msgid "**此页面的用途**"
msgstr "**What this page covers**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/mark_align_pcb.rst:6
msgid ""
"为产品定义 **mark 点（参考标记点）** 与 **独特标记（unique marker）**，使系统在每次检测前能稳定定位 PCB "
"实际位置。Mark 点用于补偿来料偏移与拼板间的微小错位；独特标记用于 A/B 面双产品检测场景下自动区分两块不同的 PCB。"
msgstr ""
"Define a product's **Mark Points** (reference marks) and **Unique Markers**,"
" so that the system can locate the actual PCB position reliably before each "
"inspection. Mark Points compensate for incoming-board shift and small "
"misalignment between sub-boards in an array; Unique Markers automatically "
"distinguish two different PCBs in A/B-side mixed-product inspection."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/mark_align_pcb.rst:8
msgid "**如何进入**"
msgstr "**How to open it**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/mark_align_pcb.rst:10
msgid "进入 **产品编程页面**（Teach），点击顶部第一个标签页 **标记 / 对齐 PCB**。"
msgstr ""
"Open the **Teach** page for a product, then click the first top tab — **Mark"
" / Align PCB**."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/mark_align_pcb.rst:-1
msgid "标记 / 对齐 PCB 主界面：左侧标记列表 + 中央 PCB 画布"
msgstr ""
"Mark / Align PCB main view: marker list on the left, PCB canvas in the "
"center."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/mark_align_pcb.rst:16
msgid "**操作流程**"
msgstr "**Workflow**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/mark_align_pcb.rst:18
msgid "**Mark 点（marker）**"
msgstr "**Mark Point (marker)**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/mark_align_pcb.rst:20
msgid ""
"点击工具栏的 **+ 标记** 按钮，在拍摄图像上框选 PCB 上固定、易识别的参考标记点（圆形 mark、矩形 "
"mark、或复杂的丝印图案均可）。绘制完成后会出现在左侧标记列表中。"
msgstr ""
"Click the **+ Mark** button on the toolbar, then drag on the captured image "
"to box a stable, easy-to-recognize reference mark on the PCB (a circular "
"mark, rectangular mark, or a complex silkscreen pattern). The new mark "
"appears in the marker list on the left."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/mark_align_pcb.rst:22
msgid "每个 mark 点都支持以下属性配置："
msgstr "Each Mark Point exposes the following options:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/mark_align_pcb.rst:24
msgid ""
"**标记形状（Shape Type）**：圆形 / 矩形 / 模板匹配。 - **圆形 / 矩形**：使用 AI 算法寻找该形状的 mark "
"点。鲁棒性强，是首选方式。 - **模板匹配（Template Match）**：直接用框内图像作为模板匹配。适合 mark "
"点表面有油墨、氧化或受光照影响导致 AI 失败时改用。"
msgstr ""
"**Shape Type**: Circle / Rectangle / Template Match. **Circle / Rectangle** "
"— uses an AI algorithm to locate a mark of that shape. Robust and the "
"preferred choice. **Template Match** — uses the image inside the ROI as a "
"template. Switch to this when the mark surface carries ink, oxidation, or "
"lighting variation that throws the AI algorithm off."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/mark_align_pcb.rst:27
msgid ""
"**二值化抽色（Mark Binarization）**：可在 mark 点底色不稳定时启用，先把 mark 点抽成二值掩膜再做匹配。开启后会出现 "
"**三色范围** 参数（X / Y / Z / A），可点击 **显示色范围 Mask** 实时预览抽色效果。"
msgstr ""
"**Mark Binarization**: enable when the mark's background color is unstable; "
"the mark is first reduced to a binary mask before matching. Enabling it "
"exposes a **Tricolor range** (X / Y / Z / A); click **Show Color Range "
"Mask** to preview the binarization live."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/mark_align_pcb.rst:28
msgid "**定位（Locate）**：让相机移动到当前 mark 点的金板位置，便于核对位置是否正确。"
msgstr ""
"**Locate**: move the camera to this Mark Point's golden-board position to "
"verify the location."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/mark_align_pcb.rst:29
msgid "**预测中心（Predict Center）**：系统重新分析当前框内图像，自动微调 mark 点中心位置；可用于消除手画时的轻微偏差。"
msgstr ""
"**Predict Center**: re-analyzes the image inside the ROI and auto-adjusts "
"the Mark Point's center; useful for cleaning up a hand-drawn box that "
"drifted slightly."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/mark_align_pcb.rst:30
msgid "**精修（Refine）**：手动微调 mark 点框的位置与大小。"
msgstr "**Refine**: manually fine-tune the Mark Point's position and size."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/mark_align_pcb.rst:32
msgid ""
"需要 **2 个 mark 点**\\ （分别置于 PCB 的对角位置）才能进行二维定位。当前版本 **最多支持 2 个 mark "
"点**，不能再添加更多。"
msgstr ""
"Two Mark Points (one in each opposite corner of the PCB) are needed for 2D "
"alignment. The current release **supports up to 2 Mark Points** — no more "
"can be added."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/mark_align_pcb.rst:-1
msgid "标记 / 对齐 PCB 画布上的 mark 点位置示意"
msgstr "Mark Point placement on the Mark / Align PCB canvas"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/mark_align_pcb.rst:38
msgid "**独特标记（unique marker）**"
msgstr "**Unique Marker**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/mark_align_pcb.rst:40
msgid ""
"仅在 **A/B 面双产品检测** 场景下需要。点击 **+ 独特标记** "
"按钮，在每个产品上框选一处与另一面差异明显的区域（例如缺口位置、专属丝印、特殊器件）。框选的区域将作为产品识别特征。"
msgstr ""
"Only needed for **A/B-side mixed-product inspection**. Click **+ Unique "
"Marker**, then box an area on each product that is visibly different from "
"the other side — a notch, a unique silkscreen, a one-of-a-kind component. "
"The selected area becomes the product's identification feature."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/mark_align_pcb.rst:42
msgid "独特标记支持选择 **分类方法**："
msgstr "Each Unique Marker can pick one of three **classification methods**:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/mark_align_pcb.rst:44
msgid "**GENERIC**：通用 AI 分类器，适合大多数差异明显的场景。"
msgstr ""
"**GENERIC**: general-purpose AI classifier, suitable when the two products "
"differ obviously."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/mark_align_pcb.rst:45
msgid "**OCV**：基于字符外观对比，适合两个产品有不同但相近的丝印文字。"
msgstr ""
"**OCV**: compares character appearance; works well when the two products "
"carry different but similar silkscreen text."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/mark_align_pcb.rst:46
msgid "**OCR**：基于字符识别，要求字符清晰、可读。"
msgstr ""
"**OCR**: relies on character recognition; the text must be clear and "
"legible."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/mark_align_pcb.rst:48
msgid "请确保所选区域在两个产品上 **差异明显**\\ （例如缺口或独有元件），否则系统在检测时可能无法可靠区分 A/B 面。"
msgstr ""
"Make sure the selected area is **visibly different** between the two "
"products (e.g. a notch or a unique component); otherwise the system may fail"
" to distinguish A/B at runtime."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/mark_align_pcb.rst:52
msgid ""
"每个产品在 A/B 面模式下需要 **正好一个** 独特标记。若该独特标记区域在两面上区分度不足，启动检测时系统会返回 **HTTP 428** "
"错误并提示重选区域。"
msgstr ""
"In A/B-side mode each product needs **exactly one** Unique Marker. If the "
"chosen region is not distinctive enough between the two sides, starting "
"inspection returns **HTTP 428** and the system prompts you to re-select the "
"area."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/mark_align_pcb.rst:54
msgid "**注意事项**"
msgstr "**Notes**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/mark_align_pcb.rst:58
msgid "**常见 Mark 点定位问题与处理建议：**"
msgstr "**Common Mark Point issues and fixes:**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/mark_align_pcb.rst:60
msgid ""
"**检测时找不到 Mark 点，报错退出**：先尝试切到 **AI 算法**（圆形/矩形），更稳定；若 mark 点表面有油墨、氧化、污渍等导致 AI "
"找圆失败，改用 **模板匹配**。"
msgstr ""
"**Mark Point not found at inspection time, aborts with error**: first try "
"the **AI algorithm** (Circle / Rectangle) — it is more robust. If ink, "
"oxidation, or contamination on the mark surface causes the AI circle finder "
"to fail, switch to **Template Match**."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/mark_align_pcb.rst:61
msgid ""
"**Mark 点找到了但定位不准 / 误报多**：检查是否板子放反（对称 mark 点可能巧合找到但定位错误）；确认两个 mark 点都画在 PCB "
"上稳定不易磨损的位置，且两点之间距离尽量大（接近对角分布），有利于精确定位旋转角度。"
msgstr ""
"**Mark Point found but localization is off / frequent false positives**: "
"check whether the board was loaded reversed (symmetric marks can be found in"
" the wrong place by coincidence). Make sure both Mark Points are on stable, "
"wear-resistant locations, and place them as far apart as possible (close to "
"opposite corners) so the rotation angle can be resolved precisely."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/mark_align_pcb.rst:62
msgid ""
"**AB 面切换后 Mark 点找不到**：先确认板子方向放置正确；单独测 B 面可以找到但 AB "
"一起测找不到，多半是独特标记选区差异不足，回到本页重新框选差异更明显的区域。"
msgstr ""
"**Mark Point can't be found after switching A/B side**: first confirm that "
"the board orientation is correct. If side B alone is found but mixed A/B "
"fails, the Unique Marker region is most likely not distinctive enough — "
"return to this page and re-select a more clearly different area."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/mark_align_pcb.rst:63
msgid ""
"**热板与冷板差异导致间歇误报**：在元件配置中适当放大 **允许偏移距离** 与 **允许旋转角度**，让对齐机制能吸收板件因温度变化产生的轻微形变。"
msgstr ""
"**Intermittent false positives between hot and cold boards**: in the "
"component configuration, increase **Allowed Shift Distance** and **Allowed "
"Rotation Angle** so the alignment mechanism can absorb the slight thermal "
"deformation of the board."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/mark_align_pcb.rst:67
msgid "**Mark 点选择建议（A 类规范）：**"
msgstr "**Mark Point selection guidelines (Class-A):**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/mark_align_pcb.rst:69
msgid "优先选择 PCB 上 **固定、不易磨损、不易被遮挡** 的圆形或矩形丝印参考点。"
msgstr ""
"Prefer **stable, wear-resistant, unobstructed** circular or rectangular "
"silkscreen reference marks on the PCB."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/mark_align_pcb.rst:70
msgid "避免选择 **元件本身**（元件可能贴歪或缺料），避免选择 **靠近 PCB 边缘** 的位置（拼接时可能被裁切）。"
msgstr ""
"Avoid using **components themselves** (a component may be skewed or missing)"
" and avoid **locations close to the PCB edge** (which can be cropped during "
"stitching)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/mark_align_pcb.rst:71
msgid "避免选择 **对称分布的 mark 点**\\ （板子放反时可能被错误识别）。"
msgstr ""
"Avoid **symmetrically placed marks** — they can be mis-identified when the "
"board is loaded reversed."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/mark_align_pcb.rst:72
msgid "每块 PCB 选择 **2 个** mark 点（当前版本上限），分别置于 PCB 的对角位置，以覆盖整板范围。"
msgstr ""
"Pick **2 Mark Points** per PCB (the current ceiling), one in each opposite "
"corner, so the pair spans the full board."

